column5: Coming from someone who has a stepdad and sees him more as a father figure then my bio dad, it’s really not up to you. You’d be a real big asshole if you told your daughter what she can and can’t call him. Also it’s not bad to have two father figures in your life. Just be a good dad that’s all you can do!
